<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Remarkable new footage showed the Hindenburg Disaster in vivid color 83 years after it exploded mid-air and caused dozens of deaths near New Jersey.</p>

<p>More than 80 years after the Hindenburg Disaster became one of the most infamous aircraft failures to date, a group upscaled the original news coverage that captured the crash and added color.</p>

<p>Neural Networks and Deep Learning first shared the altered footage on their YouTube channel, as well as their Instagram page and Patreon, in February.     </p>

